          <div class="faq">
            <div class="question">How do I Join OUIAA</div>
            <div class="answer">To join OUIAA, simply go to our Contact Us page and click the WhatsApp icon to get in touch with the alumni office directly. They’ll guide you through the process and provide all the information you need.</div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="faq">
            <div class="question">Can I request my transcript through this website?</div>
            <div class="answer">Yes. Simply go to the Transcript Request page, fill out the form, and submit the required details. You may need to upload a valid ID and provide your graduation information.</div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="faq">
            <div class="question">How can I share my success story or career journey?</div>
            <div class="answer">You can use the “Contact Us” form to tell us about your professional achievements, milestones, or unique journey after graduation. Selected stories will be featured on the website.
                </div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="faq">
            <div class="question">Is there a fee for transcript processing?</div>
            <div class="answer">Yes, transcript requests typically involve a processing fee. The exact amount and payment instructions are provided on the Transcript Request page.
            </div>
          </div>
      
          <div class="faq">
